Prerequisites : 

- Log4cxx
- Eigen3, the configure script checks for eigen3/Eigen/Dense
- HDF5, note that we need the H5Cpp bindinges for OPAQ, so be sure this is installed !

Under Ubunutu : 

sudo apt-get install libeigen3-dev libhdf5-dev libhdf5-serial-dev libhdf5-7 liblog4cxx10 liblog4cxx10-dev


usg --with-Eigen to specify a non-default path to Eigen, utested with 3.2.0